    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard to see the point of \"being the person\" when that person doesn't exist without him. everything is just gray. i look at the empty side of the bed and it feels like a permanent wound. i just wonder if it's supposed to be this hard... if i'm just supposed to keep suffering indefinitely just because i'm still here. it feels so much easier to just let go than to keep fighting this emptiness every single day.",
